## ğŸ—‚ï¸ File System Structure

Common Linux directories:

- `/` â€“ Root directory
- `/home` â€“ User home directories
- `/etc` â€“ Configuration files
- `/bin` â€“ Essential binaries
- `/var` â€“ Variable files (logs, cache)
- `/usr` â€“ User applications and files

